50.000Z","msg":"而家最驚可能係蔣麗芸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"2020隨時比人推去超區做炮灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"睇下周浩鼎同佢下次選成點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好似仲有工聯會同葉劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}